-Can he see us?
-Matty!

47:55.956 --> 47:57.499
-Is he listening?
-Matty!

47:57.583 --> 47:58.750
Matty, we're over here! Matty!

47:58.834 --> 47:59.918
-Matty!
-Hey!

48:00.043 --> 48:02.546
