48:06.925 --> 48:08.343
Matty, yes!

48:08.427 --> 48:10.470
Yes, that's right! Yes!

48:10.554 --> 48:11.763
Matty, come on!

48:12.723 --> 48:14.641
Lilly? Teddy?

48:14.725 --> 48:16.727
-Yeah, it's us!
-Come on!

48:16.810 --> 48:18.770
